" issue: when using autoindent (set ai) and (filetype plugin indent on), pasting from buffer can make extra spaces/tabs
" solution: use (set paste) before pasting and (set nopaste) when you are done
syntax enable
colorscheme delek
set background=dark
hi Search ctermfg=White ctermbg=Blue
autocmd FileType * setlocal formatoptions-=cro
nnoremap <silent> <Space> :noh<Bar>:echo<CR>
filetype plugin indent on
set number
set nowrap
set hls
set ai
set sw=4
set ts=4
set showtabline=2
set expandtab
set smarttab
